text: Helllooooo :slightly_smiling_face: so I have been applying for jobs and so far no luck haha! but I have been given some feedback on my reel by some people over at blue zoo and they said I need more character performance if I want to get into childrens tv! So i started this piece and I can see it has potential to go well but I'm stuck a bit on the timing so I was hoping you could take a look on sync sketch for me. I've only done an advanced block and there is an issue with the body popping at the end that I just cant figure out
